<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="32" type="type species">
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="32">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gory" authorityYear="1841" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavimana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Anthaxia flavimana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Gory, 1841 (subsequent designation: 
<bibRefCitation author="Chamberlin, WJ" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B18" refString="Chamberlin, WJ, 1926. Catalogue of the Buprestidae of North America north of Mexico. Chamberlin WJ, Corvallis, Oregon, 289 pp &amp; 1 page index." title="Catalogue of the Buprestidae of North America north of Mexico. Chamberlin WJ, Corvallis, Oregon, 289 pp &amp; 1 page index." year="1926">Chamberlin, 1926</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="32">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1903" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Agrilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Kerremans, C" journalOrPublisher="Elytron, Barcelona," pageId="28" pageNumber="45" refId="B26" refString="Kerremans, C, 1903. Coleoptera Serricornia. Fam. Buprestidae. Pp. 49-338. In: Wytsman P. (Ed): Genera Insectorum. Fasc. 12b, 12c, 12d. Bruxelles, Verteneuil &amp; Desmet." title="Coleoptera Serricornia. Fam. Buprestidae. Pp. 49 - 338. In: Wytsman P. (Ed): Genera Insectorum. Fasc. 12 b, 12 c, 12 d. Bruxelles, Verteneuil &amp; Desmet." year="1903">Kerremans (1903)</bibRefCitation>
and 19 mostly Neotropical species were included without designation of a type species. 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Gory" baseAuthorityYear="1841" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavimana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Agrilaxia flavimana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Gory, 1841 was subsequently designated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Chamberlin, WJ" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B18" refString="Chamberlin, WJ, 1926. Catalogue of the Buprestidae of North America north of Mexico. Chamberlin WJ, Corvallis, Oregon, 289 pp &amp; 1 page index." title="Catalogue of the Buprestidae of North America north of Mexico. Chamberlin WJ, Corvallis, Oregon, 289 pp &amp; 1 page index." year="1926">Chamberlein (1926)</bibRefCitation>
as the type species of the genus. Later on, the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1903" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Agrilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was synonymized by 
<bibRefCitation author="TheryA," journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles du Maroc," pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="21 - 53" refId="B29" refString="TheryA, , 1930. Recherches synonymiques sur les Buprestides et notes diverses. I. Note sur le genre Galbella avec descriptiones d'especes nouvelles; II. Observations concernant la preface du travail de M. Gebhardt; III. A propos de &quot;Opuscula Buprestologica&quot;. Bulletin de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles du Maroc, 10: 21 - 53" title="Recherches synonymiques sur les Buprestides et notes diverses. I. Note sur le genre Galbella avec descriptiones d'especes nouvelles; II. Observations concernant la preface du travail de M. Gebhardt; III. A propos de &quot; Opuscula Buprestologica &quot;." volume="10" year="1930">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Théry">Thery</normalizedToken>
(1930)
</bibRefCitation>
with 
<taxonomicName class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Eschscholtz, 1829, ressurected again as a valid genus by 
<bibRefCitation author="Obenberger, J" journalOrPublisher="Elytron, Barcelona," pageId="28" pageNumber="45" refId="B27" refString="Obenberger, J, 1930. Buprestidae II. Pars 111. Pp. 213-568. In: Junk W, Schenkling S (Eds) 1926-1935: Coleopterorum Catalogus, Volumen XII, Berlin - Den Haag, W. Junk, pp. 1-934." title="Buprestidae II. Pars 111. Pp. 213 - 568. In: Junk W, Schenkling S (Eds) 1926 - 1935: Coleopterorum Catalogus, Volumen XII, Berlin - Den Haag, W. Junk, pp. 1 - 934." year="1930">Obenberger (1930)</bibRefCitation>
, then finally treated as a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="5 - 235" refId="B21" refString="Cobos, A, 1972. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 16: 5 - 235" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans." volume="16" year="1972">Cobos (1972)</bibRefCitation>
; this concept was followed also by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Acta Entomologica Bohemoslovaca," pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="212 - 222" refId="B5" refString="Bily, S, 1984. Taxonomic notes on Anthaxia, with descriptions of new taxa (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Acta Entomologica Bohemoslovaca, 81: 212 - 222" title="Taxonomic notes on Anthaxia, with descriptions of new taxa (Coleoptera, Buprestidae)." volume="81" year="1984">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
(1984
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana," pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="11 - 14" refId="B7" refString="Bily, S, 1993. Two new species Anthaxia (subgen. Agrilaxia) from Mexico (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana, 1: 11 - 14" title="Two new species Anthaxia (subgen. Agrilaxia) from Mexico (Coleoptera, Buprestidae)." volume="1" year="1993">1993</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="91 - 98" refId="B14" refString="Bily, S, Bellamy, CL, 1999. The genus Agrilaxia and description of a new genus from Africa (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana 7: 91 - 98" title="The genus Agrilaxia and description of a new genus from Africa (Coleoptera: Buprestidae)." volume="7" year="1999">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
&amp; Bellamy (1999)
</bibRefCitation>
upgraded 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1903" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Agrilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
again to the generic level which was followed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B11" refString="Bily, S, 2000. A new concept of Anthaxiini (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana 8: 109-114." title="A new concept of Anthaxiini (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana 8: 109 - 114." year="2000">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
(2000
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="1 - 11" refId="B12" refString="Bily, S, 2004. Taxonomic studies on Anthaxiina Gory &amp; Laporte de Castelnau and Curina Holynski (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Zootaxa 555: 1 - 11" title="Taxonomic studies on Anthaxiina Gory &amp; Laporte de Castelnau and Curina Holynski (Coleoptera: Buprestidae)." volume="555" year="2004">2004</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<bibRefCitation author="Bellamy, CL" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B3" refString="Bellamy, CL, 2008. A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia - Moscow, pp. (1-2) + 1261-1932." title="A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia - Moscow, pp. (1 - 2) + 1261 - 1932." year="2008">Bellamy (2008)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="32">
The genus was revised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="5 - 235" refId="B21" refString="Cobos, A, 1972. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 16: 5 - 235" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans." volume="16" year="1972">Cobos (1972)</bibRefCitation>
(as a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) who described the most of the Neotropical species. Subsequently several species were described also by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Acta Entomologica Bohemoslovaca," pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="212 - 222" refId="B5" refString="Bily, S, 1984. Taxonomic notes on Anthaxia, with descriptions of new taxa (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Acta Entomologica Bohemoslovaca, 81: 212 - 222" title="Taxonomic notes on Anthaxia, with descriptions of new taxa (Coleoptera, Buprestidae)." volume="81" year="1984">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
(1984
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="International Quarterly of Entomology," pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="35 - 38" refId="B6" refString="Bily, S, 1985. Taxonomic notes on the genus Anthaxia (Col., Buprestidae) with the description of a new species from Mexico. International Quarterly of Entomology, 1: 35 - 38" title="Taxonomic notes on the genus Anthaxia (Col., Buprestidae) with the description of a new species from Mexico." volume="1" year="1985">1985</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana," pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="11 - 14" refId="B7" refString="Bily, S, 1993. Two new species Anthaxia (subgen. Agrilaxia) from Mexico (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana, 1: 11 - 14" title="Two new species Anthaxia (subgen. Agrilaxia) from Mexico (Coleoptera, Buprestidae)." volume="1" year="1993">1993</bibRefCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="1 - 5" refId="B16" refString="Bily, S, Westcott, RL, 2005. A new species of Agrilaxia from Mexico, with notes on related species (Coleoptera: Buprestidae: Anthaxiini). Folia Heyrovskyana 13: 1 - 5" title="A new species of Agrilaxia from Mexico, with notes on related species (Coleoptera: Buprestidae: Anthaxiini)." volume="13" year="2005">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
&amp; Westcott (2005)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Revista Brasileira de Biologia," pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="707 - 709" refId="B23" refString="Cobos, A, 1986. Opuscula buprestologica II - Nueva especie y nuevo sexo de Anthaxia de Mejico. Revista Brasileira de Biologia, 46: 707 - 709" title="Opuscula buprestologica II - Nueva especie y nuevo sexo de Anthaxia de Mejico." volume="46" year="1986">Cobos (1986)</bibRefCitation>
and by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B15" refString="Bily, S, Brule, S, in press. A study on the genus Agrilaxia Kerremans, 1903 of the French Guiana (Coleoptera: Buprestidae: Buprestinae: Anthaxiini). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae (in press)." title="A study on the genus Agrilaxia Kerremans, 1903 of the French Guiana (Coleoptera: Buprestidae: Buprestinae: Anthaxiini). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae (in press)." year="in press">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
&amp; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Brûlé">Brule</normalizedToken>
(in press)
</bibRefCitation>
. The morphology and the characters specific to the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1903" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Agrilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were discussed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="5 - 235" refId="B21" refString="Cobos, A, 1972. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 16: 5 - 235" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans." volume="16" year="1972">Cobos (1972)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B15" refString="Bily, S, Brule, S, in press. A study on the genus Agrilaxia Kerremans, 1903 of the French Guiana (Coleoptera: Buprestidae: Buprestinae: Anthaxiini). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae (in press)." title="A study on the genus Agrilaxia Kerremans, 1903 of the French Guiana (Coleoptera: Buprestidae: Buprestinae: Anthaxiini). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae (in press)." year="in press">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
&amp; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Brûlé">Brule</normalizedToken>
(in press)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="32">
Even after separation of some species as independent genera (see above), the genus remains still rather heterogeneous. I propose that first, the small and rather homogeneous group of species with short, green or violet, wedge shaped body should be split as the separate subgenus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bily" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Costiptera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="32">Costiptera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
subgen. nov (see below).
</paragraph>
